{"tid":661273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線新聞No.1] 踢爆保蝗党區議會唔開會是撚但畀授權票","createTime":"2018-05-11T12:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T12:59:35.000Z","uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"424e98fee409e82e146de1c6d02f3cbceef269c8","tid":661273,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=936657366507305&amp;id=153300521509664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D936657366507305%26id%3D153300521509664&d=dsmPHvEP5EPtp1H94wQWmLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=af650858\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=936657366507305&amp;id=153300521509664</a><br />\n<br />\n陳穎欣就係當時焯低民協基仔嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【區議會的授權票】<br />\n<br />\n為確保立法會議員去開會及投票，政府出動「狗仔隊」，不過區議員就自由得多，即使不開會，仍然可以投票。咩玩法？「新聞刺針」發現有區議會容許議員沒開會，但利用授權票找其他議員代投票，即使是即場的臨時動議和撥款動議都照用。議員冇開會到底知唔知自己投了咩票呢？<br />\n<br />\n【全民皆針】報料方式<br />\nWhatsApp/Telegram：66377858<br />\nInstagram：newslancet<br />\nFacebook Inbox：新聞刺針<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #新聞刺針 #區議會 #授權票 #陳穎欣 #李梓敬 #張永森"},{"pid":"adde0b7d530e9d925412f83ef50132e2b8906abf","tid":661273,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 選垃圾"},{"pid":"fd4ed22a630131f8907029a09d77d4e40d214815","tid":661273,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要mark attendance 咁都有得走堂"},{"pid":"dc70b6fe37bd37dd59e0707e5c6fe386dd5d5831","tid":661273,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"奶蝗狗做乜都唔會有事啦，再嘈乜警拉鳩埋你。"}]}